Initialize Spool in your project

Usage: spool init [OPTIONS] [PATH]

Arguments:
  [PATH]  Target directory (defaults to current directory)

Options:
      --no-color       Disable color output
      --tools <TOOLS>  Configure AI tools non-interactively (all, none, or comma-separated ids)
  -f, --force          Overwrite existing tool files without prompting
      --help-all       Print the full CLI reference (equivalent to `spool help --all`)
      --home <HOME>    Override HOME used for locating global Spool config (for parity/testing)
  -h, --help           Print help
